tYear or Month Day Year\t -->\n|other              \t=\t\t<!--\tOther grade enrollment\t -->\n|communities        \t=\t\t<!--\tCommunities served\t -->\n|feeders            \t=\t\t<!--\tFeeder schools\t -->\n|main feeder school for\t=\t\t<!--\tFeeder school for\t -->\n|footnotes          \t=\t\t<!--\tany footnotes\t -->\n|picture            \t=\t\t<!--\tPicture of the school\t -->\n|homepage           \t= {{URL|www.aurora-schools.org/1/Home}}\n}}\n\n'''Aurora High School''' is a public [[high school]] located in [[Aurora, Ohio]], United States.  It is the only high school in the [[Aurora City School District]].\n\nThe school is regularly ranked by ''[[U.S. News & World Report]]''. In 2015, it was ranked 14th in Ohio and 312th nationally.<ref>{{cite web |title=Aurora High School Overview |url=https://www.usnews.com/education/best-high-schools/ohio/districts/aurora-city/aurora-high-school-15676 |year=2015 |work=[[U.S. News & World Report]]}}</ref> In 2007, Aurora was recognized as a Blue Ribbon School by the [[National Blue Ribbon Schools Program]] with 257 other high schools.{{Citation needed|date=September 2009}}\n\n==State championships==\n* Boys' [[American football|Football]] - 2008<ref name=\"Ohio High School Athletic Association\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ohsaa.org/|title=Ohio High School Athletic Association Web site|accessdate=2008-11-29|author=[[OHSAA]]| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20081202013347/http://ohsaa.org/| archivedate= 2 December 2008 | url-status= live}}</ref>\n* Boys' [[Golf]] \u2013 1971<ref name=\"Ohio High School Athletic Association-2\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ohsaa.org/|title=Ohio High School Athletic Association Web site|accessdate=2006-12-31|author=[[OHSAA]]| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20061231042515/http://www.ohsaa.org/| archivedate= 31 December 2006 | url-status= live}}</ref>\n* Boys' [[Wrestling]] \u2013 1995<ref name=\"Yappi Wrestling\">{{cite web|url=http://www.yappi.com/statechamps/wrestling.html|title=Yappi Sports Wrestling|accessdate=2007-02-12|author=Yappi|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070113105232/http://www.yappi.com/statechamps/wrestling.html|archivedate=13 January 2007|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n==External links==\n*{{Official website|http://www.aurora-schools.org/1/Home}}\n* [http://www.aurora-schools.org Aurora City School District website]\n\n==Notes and references==\n{{reflist|2}}\n\n{{Suburban League}}\n{{Education in Portage County, Ohio|state=autocollapse}}\n\n[[Category:High schools in Portage County, Ohio]]\n[[Category:Public high schools in Ohio]]\n[[Category:Aurora, Ohio]]\n\n\n{{PortageCountyOH-school-stub}}\n", "name_user": "174.104.195.150", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aurora_High_School_(Ohio)"}
